60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"269e523bdeb368f970a38baf6b02fabec9334549","tid":1845300,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:57:34.000Z","msg":"人選擇唔死嘅原因好可能係害怕死以後嘅情況，係咪真係人死如燈滅、定係有輪迴、天堂地獄，冇人知"},{"pid":"0a6cb8ec9f2b66f220b0c1be3ff69154f68fa6eb","tid":1845300,"uid":256495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5ad3aee8e1dafdaf08c36d12acf55187be340a4","tid":1845300,"uid":247198,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"一直諗緊有咩方法係比較舒服，個結果又冇咁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T08:30:43.000Z","msg":"燒炭應該冇咁辛苦<br />\n依家天氣又咁凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd2985c202f390aec141ab8ba19c1692f2f5121","tid":1845300,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d156c44c154b34fa0e624a411879422b0940f644","tid":1845300,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:45:35.000Z","msg":"人生就是受苦 to live is to suffer<br />\n生老病死係每個人都必經 每樣都係苦<br />\n<br />\n人生每7、8樣野都係苦，得一兩樣係無咁苦<br />\n那麼生存既價值就係負數、相反死亡係零<br />\n自殺就成為較好的選擇<br />\n<br />\n就如買錯一隻沉船既股票 合理做法係止損<br />\n玩錯人生遊戲點解唔可以同樣做法？？？<br />\n<br />\n利申：學術討論 唔鼓勵人自殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:58:16.000Z","msg":"看來你心中盛載著的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀。人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，到我們的網站   <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=15b37641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（  <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=59e033f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php</a> ）。 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！"},{"pid":"691e523296fc8d4c15260817f943a9d4b84135a5","tid":1845300,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:59:17.000Z","msg":"睇自殺論"},{"pid":"ee34e7861513bee0f1c097817887f7815b996e0c","tid":1845300,"uid":247198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a6cb8ec9f2b66f220b0c1be3ff69154f68fa6eb","tid":1845300,"uid":256495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5ad3aee8e1dafdaf08c36d12acf55187be340a4","tid":1845300,"uid":247198,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"一直諗緊有咩方法係比較舒服，個結果又冇咁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T08:30:43.000Z","msg":"燒炭應該冇咁辛苦<br />\n依家天氣又咁凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"燒炭+安眠藥應該ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5d10ed6f55ceab729f2d8a06951b742fb47106","tid":1845300,"uid":247198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"830137b481b63405d0acbdd009ee6e15b9539979","tid":1845300,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5ad3aee8e1dafdaf08c36d12acf55187be340a4","tid":1845300,"uid":247198,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"一直諗緊有咩方法係比較舒服，個結果又冇咁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:51:21.000Z","msg":"吊頸0痛苦，記得去廁所先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:59:04.000Z","msg":"吊咸魚觀感麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}